{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">MODIFICA RESOLUCIONES N&#xB0; 3.413 Y N&#xB0; 3.415 EXENTAS, AMBAS DE 2021 Y DE ESTA SUBSECRETAR&#xCD;A</div></div>", "i": 10341580}, {"t": "<div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por resoluci&#xF3;n exenta N&#xB0; 1.158, de 8 de junio de 2022, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, modif&#xED;canse los numerales 1&#xB0; de la parte resolutiva de las resoluciones exentas <a href=\"https://www.leychile.cl/Navegar?idNorma=1171559&amp;idParte=&amp;idVersion=\">N&#xB0; 3.413</a> y <a href=\"https://www.leychile.cl/Navegar?idNorma=1170979&amp;idParte=&amp;idVersion=\">N&#xB0; 3.415</a>, ambas de 2021 y de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, que establecieron las toneladas asignadas a los Titulares de Licencias Transables de Pesca Clase A y Clase B, inscritas en el Registro P&#xFA;blico que lleva esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, en el sentido de modificar el monto de las cuotas anuales de captura para los recursos anchoveta a ser extra&#xED;da en la unidad de pesquer&#xED;a comprendida entre las regiones de Arica y Parinacota a Antofagasta, Anchoveta y Sardina com&#xFA;n a ser extra&#xED;das en las unidades de pesquer&#xED;as comprendidas entre las regiones de Valpara&#xED;so a Los Lagos, a&#xF1;o 2022, seg&#xFA;n se indica:</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  LTP Clase A, Anchoveta XV-II Regiones</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149703.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  LTP Clase B, Anchoveta XV-II Regiones</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149704.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149705.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149706.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149707.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  LTP Clase A, Anchoveta V-X Regiones</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149708.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  LTP Case B, Anchoveta V-X Regiones</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149709.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149710.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  LTP Clase A, Sardina com&#xFA;n V-X Regiones</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149711.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149712.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  LTP Clase B, Sardina com&#xFA;n V-X Regiones</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149713.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149714.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  <img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"Navegar/imagen/JPG/149715.jpg\"></div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbs